reviews.text:
This is most assuredly a tropical yogurt. Even having no clue what was going on, the yogurt, pineapple and coconut were vibrantly there, skirting suntan lotion territory. The vague can't place it taste makes sense that it's kiwi. Never really had one, so. I can confirm that i can taste the vanilla, and there's a good, rich mouthfeel. Like the extra touch of ws-23 to bring that cooling sensation. I actually like it in there.&#xD;
&#xD;
Did not realize I liked kiwi. Huh.
